room_title: Escape room "Sherlocked" by Escape This Madison in Madison
room_description: What a relaxing evening... or so you thought. Instead, you find yourself at the center of one of his "experiments”, a game of sorts that only Sherlock could have created. Your powers of deduction will be put to the test in this eccentric and carefully crafted rite-of-passage. It’s elementary, so he says, or is it?
